{{Top|canon=NK-3 medium ion cannon}}
The '''NK-3 ion cannon''' was a type of [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]]-scale [[Ion cannon/Legends|ion cannon]] that was manufactured by [[Borstel Galactic Defense/Legends|Borstel Galactic Defense]]. [[Cygnus Spaceworks/Legends|Cygnus Spaceworks]] utilized the NK-3 weapons system on its [[Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wing/Legends|Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wings]], as did [[Sienar Fleet Systems/Legends|Sienar Fleet Systems]] for their [[TIE/d "Defender" Multi-Role Starfighter/Legends|TIE/D Defenders]], both of which saw service with the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. Both the TIE Defender and the Star Wings carried two of these cannons, which they used to disable other craft.

